headline: Wolters Kluwer Announces Winners of 2025 Legal Innovator Awards
summary: HOUSTON, November 06, 2025--Wolters Kluwer Legal & Regulatory’s ELM Solutions is proud to announce HCA Healthcare and Whataburger as the winners of its annual Legal Innovator Awards. The awards were presented during Amplify 2025, the company’s premier user conference held at the JW Marriott Orlando Bonnet Creek Resort & Spa.
